Profile: TrustEvidenceReceipt
Parent: Basic
Id: trustevidence-receipt
Title: "TrustEvidence receipt"
Description: "Draft Basic profile representing a compact receipt emitted by a TrustEvidence backend. It is used only for local validation of synthetic evidence commitments."
* extension contains TEBackendType named backendType 1..1 and TEEvidenceHash named evidenceHash 1..1 and TEReceiptRoot named receiptRoot 1..1 and TEPolicyVersion named policyVersion 0..1
* code 1..1
